translated: Mångberg, Sven Ollof Andreiais, fire chief, Vänersborg, born September 27, 1881, in Umeå to parents Enik Ollof M. and Maria Tuneflili G. Married to Esther Kristenson. Children: Cardi-Erdik (born 1923), Gunnar (born 1926). Former occupations: technician in Örebro (1901), engineer at Robiertisifors Brnik (1902-1907), at Ytterstfor's Bruk in Bysike (1907-1910), at Umeå City Building Office (1910-1913), at Failkenberigis (1913-1919), and at Vänersborg City (1919-1946). Appointed fire chief of Vänersborg in 1924. Board member in Älvsborg (1911), Fire Brigade Association (since 1927), and Vänersborg City Administration Association (1931-1933). Active in the Swedish Fire Brigade Association, Swedish Air Defense Association, and Bridge Club.
